DOC.brief_summary: To compare concurrent membrane sweeping with dinoprostone versus dinoprostone in labor induction for nulliparas at term with an unfavorable cervix
DOC.brief_title: Concurrent Membrane Sweeping With Dinoprostone Versus Dinoprostone in Labor Induction of Nulliparas at Term With an Unfavorable Cervix
DOC.criteria: singleton pregnancy Nulliparous women gestational age >=37.0 weeks Bishop score <=6 intact amniotic membrane absence of labor live fetus with vertex presentation no previous uterine surgical procedure Multiple pregnancy Placenta previa
